/**
 * WasmOpcode.ets — Centralized WebAssembly instruction definitions.
 * Single source of truth for ALL opcodes, categories, and metadata.
 * Designed for future VMP (Virtual Machine Protection) code development.
 *
 * Based on: WAMR core/iwasm/interpreter/wasm_opcode.h
 * Mirrors all opcodes from the 5 enums (WASMOpcode, WASMGCEXTOpcode,
 * WASMMiscEXTOpcode, WASMSimdEXTOpcode, WASMAtomicEXTOpcode).
 */

